name: Ikumi Mito (Food Wars!) TI
description:
My second TI, This time ikumi mito from food wars! trained on 200 images from the anime(season 1+ova) at 14k steps.

Works best when you put masterpiece, best quality and even ultra quality in the positive prompt.

Images were made using anything-v4.5-pruned

prompt to generate character: Ikumi_Mito

Very cleavage prone as that's how the character dresses so if you want a closed shirt you might need to add extra tags like: buttoned up shirt, closed shirt etc..

Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/embeddings
